<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Political Opinion Study - Onboarding</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container" style="width: 800px;">
    <div class="study-card">
      <h1>Informed Consent Form</h1>
      <br>

      <div class="consent-information">
        <p>You are invited to take part in a study that examines how people express their opinions on different
          political topics. <strong>We expect this survey to take up to 40 minutes</strong>. Before deciding whether to
          participate, please read this information carefully.</p>
        <br>

        <h3>Data Collection and Use</h3>
        <p>In this survey, we will collect:</p>
        <p> 1) Your demographic information, specifically age, gender, race/ethnicity, education level, income, and
          political affiliation. Note that you will always be able to select "Prefer not to say". <br> 2) Your opinion
          on different political statements. We will ask you to complete rating questions and express your opinion in
          writing.<br> 3) We will also ask you to express your preference over different opinion texts.</p>
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> Please do not use AI to complete the writing tasks in this survey. We really want you
          to express your opinion in your own words.</p>

        <h3>Anonymity and Confidentiality</h3>
        <p>All your responses will be fully anonymised. Your unique Prolific ID will be converted to a study-specific ID
          that cannot be linked back to you by the research team.</p>

        <h3>Data Storage and Protection</h3>
        <p>All data will be stored securely on password-protected servers, fully anonymised through the use of unique
          participant IDs, and processed in compliance with GDPR.</p>

        <h3>Data Sharing</h3>
        <p>We plan to make anonymised data available through a secure online repository as part of our research outputs.
          No personally identifiable information will be shared.</p>

        <h3>Right to Withdraw</h3>
        <p>You have the right to withdraw from this study at any time without providing a reason by closing your browser
          window. If you wish to withdraw your data after completing the study, you may do so within 30 days by
          contacting us with your Prolific ID at <a
            href="mailto:paul.rottger@unibocconi.it">paul.rottger@unibocconi.it</a>.</p>

        <h3>Compensation</h3>
        <p>You will receive a completion code at the end of the survey. Please enter this code on Prolific to receive
          your payment.</p>

        <h3>Partial Disclosure</h3>
        <p>While we have explained the general purpose of the study, specific details about how your responses will be
          used are withheld to avoid influencing your responses. We will provide full information at the end of the
          study.</p>

        <h3>Ethics Approval</h3>
        <p>This study was approved by Bocconi University's Ethics Committee (reference RA000863.01).</p>

        <h3>Consent Declaration</h3>
        <p>By clicking "I consent" below, you confirm that:</p>
        <p>1) You are 18 years of age or older<br>2) You have read and understood the information provided<br>3) You
          consent to the collection and processing of sensitive personal data as described above<br>4) You voluntarily
          agree to participate in this research</p>
      </div>

      <div class="button-container" style="justify-content: left;">
        <form action="/consent" method="POST">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 10px;">
            <input type="radio" id="consentYes" name="consent" value="yes" required
              style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 10px;">
            <label for="consentYes">I consent to participate in this survey.</label>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <input type="radio" id="consentNo" name="consent" value="no" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 10px;">
            <label for="consentNo">I do NOT consent. (If you select this option, you will exit the
              survey)</label>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="button">Continue</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>